name: Day Three All Around End The Week Workout

workouts.name: High knees + Boxing
workouts.description: Stand tall and run in place, bringing knees up to hip level while punching arms forward

workouts.name: Push-ups + Side Turn
workouts.description: Start in a push-up position, perform a push-up, then rotate to one side and extend the top arm

workouts.name: Bicycle Abs
workouts.description: Lie on your back, lift legs to 90 degrees, and alternate bringing knees to chest while extending the opposite leg

workouts.name: Alternating Lunges
workouts.description: Step forward with one leg, lowering hips until both knees are bent at about a 90-degree angle

workouts.name: Mountain Climbers
workouts.description: Start in a plank position, alternate bringing knees to chest quickly as if running in place

workouts.name: Dips
workouts.description: Start in a seated position with hands on the edge of a bench, lower body towards the ground and then push back up
